The membership fees are based on residency within Temple Terrace city limits.  Call 813.506.6600 for payment information. Payments must be made in person. Guest Policy Adult members may bring guests at the discretion of the Parks and Recreation Division. Guests must be accompanied by an adult member at all times. Maximum of 5 guests per family membership and 2 guests allowed per individual membership per day. Minor members (17 & under) cannot bring a guest without an adult member present at all times. AN ID AND A SIGNED WAIVER ARE REQUIRED TO PURCHASE A DAILY GUEST PASS. THE WAIVER CAN BE FILLED OUT HERE. Upon arrival at the Family Recreation Complex, please inform the front desk staff that you have completed the waiver online. All guests coming to the Family Rec Complex must have a completed Liability Waiver on file with the City. If a member is bringing a non-family member 17 years of age or younger, the minor's legal guardian must fill out the form prior to arrival. The forms may either be printed and brought to the Complex or filled out online and submitted via email prior to the visit.
